  {panel}

Currently, user-picker in Service Desk portal are hard-coded to only show 10 possible match. If the user based is huge there are some user that is not searchable even though if we search using whole username.

h4.Suggestion
Make user-picker limit to be configurable or follow JIRA user picker which have limit of 20 users.
